        "javadoc": "/**\n * Copies source to dest.\n * <p>Neither source nor dest can be null.</p>\n *\n * @param source SummaryStatistics to copy\n * @param dest SummaryStatistics to copy to\n * @throws NullArgumentException if either source or dest is null\n */\n",
